description: Joe Biden's domestic in-tray means neither a UK trade deal nor EU relations will be top priority.
title: US election: What does Joe Biden's win mean for Brexit Britain and Europe?
title_page: US election: What does Joe Biden's win mean for Brexit Britain and Europe? - BBC News
maintext: As for the idea that the Biden administration will focus primarily on Paris and Berlin, rather than London, since the UK can no longer serve as a useful bridge between the US and EU, those close to the president-elect say he'll want to nurture all those relations - and those with Brussels directly too. It's not a matter of one more than the other.
